export const lightTheme = {
    name: "light",
    backgroundPrimary: "linear-gradient(rgba(254, 133, 138, 80), rgba(254, 133, 138, 40),  rgba(254, 133, 138, 20), rgba(254, 133, 138, 10)   ,rgba(254, 133, 138, 2));",
    backgroundSecondary: "#FFFFFF",
    textColor: "rgba(85, 72, 76, 0.9)",
    borderColor: "#FE858A",
    backgroundForm: "linear-gradient(to bottom , pink, var(--pink1), var(--pink1), var(--pink1),var(--pink1));",
    backgroundPrimaryButton: "linear-gradient(rgba(85, 72, 76, 80), rgba(85, 72, 76, 40), rgba(85, 72, 76, 20), rgba(85, 72, 76, 10), rgba(85, 72, 76, 2));",

}

export const darkTheme = {
    name: "dark",
    backgroundPrimary: "linear-gradient(rgba(85, 72, 76, 80), rgba(85, 72, 76, 40), rgba(85, 72, 76, 20), rgba(85, 72, 76, 10), rgba(85, 72, 76, 2));",
    backgroundSecondary: "rgba(85, 72, 76, 0.9)",
    textColor: "#FFFFFF",
    borderColor: "#FFFFFF",
    backgroundForm: "linear-gradient(to bottom,rgba(85, 72, 76, 80),rgba(85, 72, 76, 80),rgba(85, 72, 76, 80),rgba(85, 72, 76, 80),rgba(85, 72, 76, 40));",
    backgroundPrimaryButton: "linear-gradient(rgba(254, 133, 138, 80), rgba(254, 133, 138, 40),  rgba(254, 133, 138, 20), rgba(254, 133, 138, 10)   ,rgba(254, 133, 138, 2));",
}
